      • parseFile

        public static UntypedTree parseFile(String fname,
                                    String grammarName,
                                    String startSymbol,
                                    String prefix)
        Parses the file fname with the ANTLR grammar grammarName (which must be fully qualified with the package name).
        Parameters:
        fname - name of file to be parsed
        grammarName - name of the ANTLR grammar. Corresponding lexer and praser are loaded reflectively.
        startSymbol - start symbol in the grammar. Corresponding method in the parser is loaded reflectively.
        prefix - adds the prefix as the first token in any sub serailized tree
        Returns:
        the untyped tree generated by the parser
